  "Orbital Construction Yard": {"s":48,"t":"D","y":["Phobolog","Saturn Systems","Io Mining Industries","Titan Shuttles"],"w":"When you have multiple space cards in hand. Skip if your hand is building/earth-focused or if AMC risk is high.","e":"1 ti-prod = 12"},
  "Board of Directors": {"s":55,"t":"C","y":["Applied Science","Point Luna","Viron","Restricted Area"],"w":"Когда вам нужен card draw pipeline и Earth тег. Лучше с Point Luna. Не приоритетная — immediate value слишком мала дл...","e":"4 director resources"},
  "Self-Sufficient Settlement": {"s":53,"t":"D","y":["Tharsis Republic","Rover Construction","Capital"],"w":"Only for Mayor milestone on Tharsis or prime city spot on Elysium. Otherwise skip.","e":"2 MC-prod = 10-12 MC, city tile = ~5-10 MC"},
  "Anti-desertification Techniques": {"s":52,"t":"D","y":["Ecoline","Splice","Tharsis Republic"],"w":"Only when tags matter for your strategy (Ecologist, Splice) and other preludes are worse. Generally skip.","e":"1 plant-prod = 8 MC, 1 steel-prod = 8 MC, 3 MC immediate"},
