  "Mohole Excavation": {"s":48,"t":"D","y":["Helion","Robotic Workforce","Electro Catapult"],"w":"Almost never. Only as Helion or if you need Building tag and nothing better exists.","e":"1 steel-prod = 8 MC, 2 heat-prod = 8 MC, 2 heat = ~1 MC"},
  "Preservation Program": {"s":48,"t":"D","y":["Terraforming Deal"],"w":"При pure TR rush, когда 5 TR ставят вас close к Terraformer milestone. Сочетается с Terraforming Deal (+10 MC from ef...","e":"5 TR = 5 MC-prod + 5 VP = ~35 MC (5 x 7 MC)"},
