  "Nobel Prize": {"s":45,"t":"D","y":["Research Coordination","Solarnet"],"w":"Almost never. Production preludes are strictly better for gen 1. Only if other options are terrible.","e":"5 MC + 2 VP (= ~10 MC mid-game) + 2 requirement cards (~8 MC from selection) + Wild tag ~2 MC"},
