  "Insects": {"s":88,"t":"A","y":["Ecological Zone","Viral Enhancers","Heather","Lichen"],"w":"Always high draft priority. Keep from opening hand with ANY plant tags. Even hate-draft to deny plant players. Top 10...","e":"9 MC + 3 MC card = 12 MC"},
