  "Media Group": {"s":76,"t":"B","y":["Optimal Aerobraking","Nuclear Zone"],"w":"Early game with events in hand. Even mid-game it's good if you expect 3+ more events. High draft priority.","e":"Cost 6+3=9 MC"},
