  "Red Ships": {"s":75,"t":"B","y":["Corridors of Power","Rise To Power","Cultural Metropolis"],"w":"Gen 1-3 when parameters are low. Always pick if offered early -- the ROI is absurd for 5 MC. Becomes unplayable gen 6+.","e":"2+3=5 MC total"},
