  "GMO Contract": {"s":74,"t":"B","y":["Ecological Zone","Viral Enhancers","Decomposers","Topsoil Contract"],"w":"Gen 1-3 with planned bio-tag strategy and Greens accessible. Excellent return even with 3-4 future bio tags.","e":"3 MC + 3 MC card = 6 MC cost"},
  "Homeostasis Bureau": {"s":74,"t":"B","y":["Deimos Down","GIA","Standard Tech","Credicor"],"w":"Early game when planning to terraform via heat. Excellent gen 1-3 play. Loses value if temperature is already near max.","e":"16 MC + 3 MC card = 19 MC"},
  "Lunar Exports": {"s":74,"t":"B","y":["Phobolog","Earth Office","Acquired Space Agency"],"w":"Gen 1-3 for MC production mode. Ti-payable makes it excellent with prelude titanium. Almost always take MC over plants.","e":"19 MC + 3 MC card = 22 MC for 5 MC-prod (~25 MC) or 2 plant-prod (~16 MC)"},
  "Meat Industry": {"s":74,"t":"B","y":["Ecological Zone","Martian Zoo","Birds","Fish","Miranda colony"],"w":"When you have 1+ VP animal cards or Ecological Zone. With Miranda colony in play it becomes very strong. Don't draft ...","e":"Cost 5+3=8 MC (steel payable)"},
